OL,3,CPolice issue warning to parents after
OL,4,Cfires were started
OL,6,FCumbria Police have warned parents
OL,7,Fabout the risk of fires after the Fire
OL,8,Fand Rescue Service received several
OL,9,Freports over the weekend.
OL,11,FCarlisle East Fire Station was called
OL,12,Fa number of times in response to fires
OL,13,Fbeing started in Currock and Upperby
OL,14,Fon 24 August 2024.
OL,16,FCarlisle Police have issued a caution
OL,17,Fto parents on social media.
