OL,3,CPolice issue warning to parents after
OL,4,Cfires were started
OL,6,FIn a statement, they said: "Acts of
OL,7,Fsetting fires, regardless of the
OL,8,Flocation carry a high risk of causing
OL,9,Fharm to those carrying out the acts
OL,10,Fand members of the public.
OL,12,F"As such the offence of arson carries
OL,13,Fa substantial sentence in the courts.
OL,15,F"Officers from your local
OL,16,FNeighbourhood teams will be out in
OL,17,Fthese areas in marked vehicles and
OL,18,Fplain clothes to provide reassurance
OL,19,Fto local residents.
