OL,3,CPolice issue warning to parents after
OL,4,Cfires were started
OL,6,F"When identified those responsible
OL,7,Fface substantial sanctions and we will
OL,8,Flook to work with partners such as
OL,9,FRiverside Group to deliver a lasting
OL,10,Fdisruption to any criminality
OL,11,Fidentified.
OL,13,F"Parents, if your child is returning
OL,14,Fhome smelling of smoke you must have a
OL,15,Fconversation around the risk
OL,16,Fassociated with this behaviour before
OL,17,Fyour child's actions impact you or
OL,18,Fworse."
